snippet.textDisplay: I was really excited to hear this. The singers have great voice and a fair bit of musical talent. I just don't think the overall music composition works. snippet.textDisplay: People say “out of sight out of mind”.it’s lowkey true.but we can sense the actual essence of love when we can feel the same intensity and care in long distance.otherwise it’s nothing else a allure.and cause of this long distance,many heart break occurs.for many people love is only about sexual desire though it’s part of love and in somehow convenient but care,affection and respect is most important to build up a true and strong relationship.
